2026-05-13T16:57:34.1942360Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-13T16:57:34.1943057Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-13T16:57:34.1943928Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-13T16:57:34.1944786Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-13T16:57:34.1954059Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-13T16:57:34.1973886Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-13T16:57:34.1994674Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-13T16:57:34.2024117Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-13T16:57:34.2056839Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-13T16:57:34.2083865Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-13T16:57:34.2103980Z 33    -->
2026-05-13T16:57:34.2174107Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
2026-05-13T16:57:34.2194110Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:5-79
2026-05-13T16:57:34.2225059Z 34-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:29:22-76
2026-05-13T16:57:34.2264053Z 35    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.USE_EXACT_ALARM" />
