2026-05-13T16:57:34.2338066Z 38        Used on Samsung and other OEM devices that aggressively optimize
2026-05-13T16:57:34.2338930Z 39        battery usage. MainActivity shows a one-time dialog that opens
2026-05-13T16:57:34.2339790Z 40        the system "ignore battery optimizations" screen so scheduled
2026-05-13T16:57:34.2340510Z 41        reminders are not deferred indefinitely.
